hidden_gems_uniform_exploration.title: Something Completely Different
hidden_gems_uniform_exploration.description: We picked these out just for you.

289779.title: 5th Street
289779.description: A husband in inner-city Los Angeles is determined to track down the gang responsible for murdering his wife in this gritty action thriller.

300445.title: All Dogs Go to Heaven
300445.description: After being betrayed by his partner in crime, a dog cons his way out of Heaven to get revenge, teaming up with an orphan who can talk to animals.

300459.title: Not Without My Daughter
300459.description: In this thriller based on a true story, an Iranian-American man takes his American wife and daughter to visit Iran, only to keep them hostage there.

300461.title: Quigley Down Under
300461.description: A man hired as a sharpshooter travels to Australia, where he learns his new, high-paying job has a morbid catch that leaves him conflicted.

302326.title: Gang Related
302326.description: Two men face the consequences after they kill a man and pin the murder on an innocent transient.

302505.title: The Substitute
302505.description: Undercover as a substitute teacher, an ex-marine cleans up the crime-infested school when he discovers a gang tormenting students and staff.

304808.title: She-Devil
304808.description: A popular romance novelist embarks on an affair with his accountant, which proves to be the last straw for his disgruntled suburban wife.

305818.title: Harley Davidson And The Marlboro Man
305818.description: Two modern-day "Robin Hoods" heist an armored car full of drugs, putting them in the sights of hired killers and on a ride for their lives.

307753.title: Kickboxer
307753.description: After a kickboxing champ is paralyzed fighting Thailand’s top fighter, his brother vows vengeance but must learn Muay Thai to fight back.

348935.title: Frozen
348935.description: Three skiers find themselves stuck on a chairlift above the frigid slopes. Their attempts to escape may prove deadlier than the cold itself.

356526.title: Be Cool
356526.description: Chili Palmer turns to the world of rock stars, pop divas, and hip hop gangstas when a new idea for a movie leads him into the music business.

367706.title: Jailbait
367706.description: She killed her stepfather in self-defense. Now, Anna must fight her dark side and survive the world of girl gangs and predatory guards in juvy.

367819.title: Titanic 2
367819.description: A century after the fateful voyage of the original, modern luxury liner Titanic II sets sail. Will this ship suffer the same fate as her namesake?

389506.title: Robocop 2
389506.description: In a dystopian Detroit, drug dealers run rampant. Cyborg cop Alex Murphy returns to take on both a crime boss and a twisted version of his own self.

404581.title: Hit and Run
404581.description: A college student discovers a man's nearly dead body impaled on her Jeep and makes a series of fateful decisions as he comes back to terrorize her.

439500.title: Vanishing on 7th Street
439500.description: Detroit is a ghost town after a strange blackout. A few strangers remain and, as each day grows shorter, they discover the enemy is darkness itself.

451668.title: Miss Meadows
451668.description: Miss Meadows is a just a prim school teacher on the outside but inside hides the soul of a vigilante, righting wrongs by whatever means necessary.

461203.title: Instructions Not Included
461203.description: An Acapulco playboy's life turns upside down when a former fling leaves a baby on his doorstep, and he has to raise the child on his own.

463206.title: El Pistolero
463206.description: Un poderoso llega a un pueblo en busca de nuevos pistoleros para su equipo y un hombre sencillo acepta el trabajo para vengar la muerte de su padre.

464287.title: Forgiveness
464287.description: A beloved Pastor works to serve his 'flock' and save his church. In his dedication and desire to do so, he crosses uncrossable boundaries.

465867.title: Baytown Outlaws
465867.description: In the fight for her godson after being taken, a woman hires three outlaw, redneck brothers to bring him back to her.

473244.title: Falcon Rising
473244.description: After his sister is attacked by gangsters in Brazil, a dangerous man systematically stomps his way through thugs and crooks to get revenge.

475828.title: Total Eclipse
475828.description: Annihilation is on the line as a manned space station is hit by a meteor, crashing through space towards Los Angeles, with a nuclear reactor onboard.

478811.title: Six Reasons Why
478811.description: Four men standoff with guns drawn in the Badlands. Their stories are filled with secrets, revenge, and even murder. Who will live to tell these tales?

486556.title: A Home of Our Own
486556.description: Frances and her six children are looking for a fresh start. They spot an unfinished house and do whatever it takes to build a home of their own.

486566.title: Over the Top
486566.description: A truck driver attempts to reconnect with his estranged son as he road trips to Las Vegas to compete in an arm wrestling championship.

489902.title: Jeff Dunham: Arguing With Myself
489902.description: Join Jeff and his outspoken felt pals: Walter, Peanut, José Jalapeño, Bubba J, and Sweet Daddy Dee for an evening of laughs and observations.

493084.title: Life on the Line
493084.description: With a huge storm barreling down on their hometown, a team of brave linemen risk it all to make sure essential services stay online.

494842.title: Shottas
494842.description: Two young men from Jamaica climb to the top of the criminal world in Miami, with a constant presence of drugs, extortion, and deceit.

496421.title: Dangerous Intentions
496421.description: A battered woman has no allies in her family or the legal system. The danger of escape is vivid after her friend is killed by her own abusive husband.

507469.title: August: Osage County
507469.description: A dysfunctional mother’s emotional wounds against her adult children come to light as her family arrives at her Oklahoma home after a relative dies.

507677.title: Absolution
507677.description: A girl born with the power to absorb the pain and fear of others has to maximize it to save the man she loves while being guided by those she’s saved.

507844.title: After Dark
507844.description: Based on true events, a spring break trip turns tragic when a flat tire and a sinister drifter come before a night that the friends may not survive

512448.title: New Jack City
512448.description: Two streetwise cops embark on the riskiest mission of their careers when they go undercover to bust a ruthless drug kingpin reigning over Harlem.

519423.title: Earthfall
519423.description: When a massive asteroid pulls Earth out of orbit and wreaks chaos on the ground, one man uncovers the secret government plan that could save humanity.

520071.title: The Secret Path
520071.description: A 14-year-old Southern girl is forced into a life of prostitution by her grandpa. Her only joy comes from her supportive African-American friends.

520213.title: Train to Busan (Dubbed)
520213.description: A father and his estranged daughter are trapped on a speeding train full of fellow passengers when a zombie virus breaks out in South Korea.

521601.title: Recoil
521601.description: After arriving in a gang-controlled Washington town, an ex-cop seeks to avenge his family by tracking down the gang members who killed them.

521969.title: 88 Minutes
521969.description: A forensic psychiatrist, whose testimony has put away numerous criminal defendants, gets a death threat with just 88 minutes to find his killer.

527970.title: Blitz
527970.description: A tough cop and his sidekick, who faces ridicule from their homophobic squad, are dispatched to take down a serial killer who targets the police.

528587.title: Look Who's Talking Now
528587.description: In this third chapter of the series, it is not just the kids who are talking, when the family’s favorite canines bring love and chaos into their lives

528603.title: Juwanna Mann
528603.description: After a basketball star is booted out of the NBA when his on-court antics go too far, he poses as a woman and joins the WUBA.

528667.title: When the Bough Breaks
528667.description: The trust between a married couple and the woman carrying their child is torn when the surrogate decides she wants the husband and baby for herself.

530157.title: Cupid
530157.description: After mean girls humiliate her at school, a practicing witch summons evil Cupid to take revenge and turn the walls red with blood for Valentine’s Day.

545561.title: Orphan
545561.description: A couple mourning the loss of their unborn baby adopt a little girl, except her new mom suspects something is disturbingly wrong with the child.

557272.title: Letters From the Heart
557272.description: When Hope travels to a small town for her grandmother’s funeral, she learns that she’s inherited two million dollars, under one condition.

557537.title: 16 and Missing
557537.description: An FBI agent must save her 16-year-old daughter after she runs away to meet an older man she met online.

559207.title: The Trees Have Eyes
559207.description: On the trail of an escaped killer in the New England woods, a group of bounty hunters becomes the hunted when they stumble into a lair of the undead.

569769.title: Pandorum
569769.description: Panic and terror come fast as two astronauts wake up in an empty spacecraft with no memory of what happened - except that an evil entity is waiting.

572750.title: The Blackout: Invasion Earth
572750.description: A military crew discovers an outpost of survivors surrounded by corpses, from cars to hospitals, and tries to find out the cause of the mass deaths.

579298.title: Tyler Perry's Madea's Witness Protection
579298.description: The law’s takedown of a Wall Street banker who ran a Ponzi scheme is nothing compared to having to live with his family in hiding at Madea’s house!

581251.title: The Long Walk Home
581251.description: Set in 1955 Montgomery, Alabama, this is the story of two women who must decide how they will respond to Martin Luther King Jr.’s call to boycott.

581300.title: Diana
581300.description: The bedroom of an apartment in Paseo de la Castellana, Madrid. It is Sofia's bedroom, a deluxe escort. Her new client discovers the name that is tattoed on her leg 'Diana'... Is it your real name?' He introduced himself as Hugo, but his real name is Jano. Who is really Sofia? According to an interview aired on an investigative tv program, 'a social waste, a victim who didn't know how to survive the economic crisis'. Who is Jano? Society portrays him as a symbol of the entrepreneur of the future, an example to follow. Sofia's apartment becomes the stage where the personality or personalities of both will be revealed as onion layers until reaching the core. And the key to Sofia's is to discover who is Diana and what does she mean to her...

586151.title: The Andromeda Strain (1971)
586151.description: Follow Michael Crichton’s intense story of a scientific team working around the clock to stop an alien germ brought back by a space probe.

587321.title: Occupation
587321.description: When alien invaders threaten mankind, a group of random townspeople must band together and fight back against the vicious extraterrestrials.

589013.title: Dirty 30
589013.description: The simple 30th birthday celebration Kate agreed to with a small group of friends quickly spirals out of control when unexpected guests arrive.

589177.title: Money Talks
589177.description: A con man, in need of protection from the cops, the mob, and his pregnant girlfriend, joins forces with a struggling TV newsman in need of a story.

589380.title: Dennis the Menace
589380.description: Based on the beloved comic strip, a well-meaning but wholly destructive little boy unwittingly wreaks mayhem upon his surly next-door neighbor.

592462.title: Where She Lies
592462.description: An assaulted American teen in the early 1960s gives birth and is told her baby died until decades later a deathbed confession changes that reality.

597948.title: La Francotiradora (Español)
597948.description: Lyudmila, una destacada francotiradora rusa, se encuentra en peligro después de que un alto comandante alemán ordena eliminarla a cualquier precio.

604336.title: Who's Your Caddy?
604336.description: When superstar rap mogul C-Note tries to join the Carolina Pines Golf & Country Club, the establishment's snooty members greet him with opposition.

609489.title: The Humanity Bureau
609489.description: Nicolas Cage stars as a case agent in the year 2030 out to save a mother and son in the climate ravaged Midwest whom the government has exiled.

610961.title: High Crimes
610961.description: When a savvy lawyer learns her husband is roped into a possible government conspiracy, she gets help in her investigation from a veteran military attorney.

610966.title: The League of Extraordinary Gentlemen
610966.description: A team of fantastical superheroes from literary tales are assembled by a notorious adventurer in order to save the planet from annihilation.

613517.title: Bobbi Kristina
613517.description: This drama depicts the turbulent life and struggles faced by the daughter of high-profile singers Whitney Houston and Bobby Brown.

618279.title: Ace Ventura: When Nature Calls
618279.description: Jim Carrey returns in this hilarious sequel as Ace Ventura, back from a spiritual quest and on the case to find a rare and sacred white African bat.

621292.title: Black Dog
621292.description: An ex-convict truck driver with makes one last no-questions-asked trip, only to discover that his rig is stocked with assault weapons.

625413.title: The Scorpion King: Book of Souls
625413.description: When an evil warlord gains a sword that can steal souls, the Scorpion King and the sister of a Nubian king must find the one thing that can stop him.

626763.title: Above Suspicion
626763.description: “Game of Thrones” star Emilia Clarke leads this true crime thriller as an informant whose help with an FBI agent leads to a deadly aftermath.

628012.title: Blue Ridge
628012.description: When a murder shocks a small town, an old feud reignites and a new sheriff must solve the crime before the locals take the law into their own hands.

634430.title: The Healer
634430.description: With the help of a teenage girl with terminal cancer, Alec Bailey learns to embrace and put to use his family’s mysterious gift of healing people.

636625.title: El Diablo, El Santo Y El Tonto
636625.description: Antes de morir, un viejo hacendado le revela a su hijo que tiene otros dos hijos, a quienes deberá buscar para dividirse la herencia entre los tres.

638893.title: Deliver Us From Eva
638893.description: The formidable Eva Dandridge is considered an angel by her sisters, but their men think she’s a devil. Can a new suave player win her heart?

639245.title: El Hijo Del Pueblo
639245.description: Como no se halla en su vida de taxista ni con la gente de ciudad, se regresó a su rancho, donde accidentalmente cae una avioneta llena de gente bien.

639856.title: The Lies He Told
639856.description: The true story of a charming military man, who arranges his own disappearance and fakes his death, to begin a new life with an unsuspecting woman.

644879.title: Big Jake
644879.description: John Wayne and Maureen O’Hara reunite in this Western about a no-nonsense rancher who hunts down the outlaw gang that abducted his grandson.

646627.title: One Bad Habit
646627.description: A tight-knit group of friends, each in their own toxic relationships, come to realize that putting the kibosh on those relationships won’t end well.

656926.title: Pretty Obsession
656926.description: A pretty eighteen year-old puts herself and her family in danger when she leads a double life as an erotic web cam model.

657079.title: Let's Go to Prison
657079.description: When Fate steers a career criminal’s plot for revenge off-course, he sends his intended victim’s kid to prison, and then joins him in the slammer.

657981.title: Trust Nobody
657981.description: A young hustler's untamed thirst for power can make him destroy his own family while a woman's greed can cause her to do the unthinkable.

660332.title: Ann Rule's Everything She Ever Wanted
660332.description: A sensual, self-assured Southern belle uses her easily influenced husband, and any other means necessary, to ascend the ranks of Atlanta's elite.

662071.title: Malibu Shark Attack
662071.description: A tsunami floods Malibu and unleashes a hunting pack of sharks, trapping a group of lifeguards and a team of construction workers in high water.

672282.title: Jumanji
672282.description: Two children find and play a magical board game, releasing a man who has been trapped in it for decades and a host of wild and exotic creatures.

672284.title: Pixels
672284.description: An unlikely group of former '80s video game champions step up to save the world from an alien invasion in this visually spectacular action-adventure.

676450.title: Guilty
676450.description: A sexual assault allegation made by a fellow student against her high school science teacher lures 17-year-old Traci into a web of deception.

676725.title: Boyhood
676725.description: Richard Linklater's acclaimed hit, filmed over twelve years with the same cast, is a groundbreaking celebration of life, growing up, and parenting.

682626.title: Get Him to the Greek
682626.description: Aspiring music exec Aaron Green has just 72 hours to deliver rock legend Aldous Snow to LA, navigating a minefield of mayhem to get there.

686299.title: She's Too Young
686299.description: The repercussions of teenage sexuality are explored when a 14-year-old Halifax girl succumbs to peer pressure and the attention of an older boy.

696806.title: A Walk to Remember
696806.description: North Carolina teens Landon Carter and Jamie Sullivan are thrown together after one gets into trouble and is sentenced to community service.

698996.title: After the Silence
698996.description: An abused 20-year-old deaf woman who was never taught sign language is rescued by a social worker who takes her in and teaches her how to communicate.

699012.title: One of Her Own
699012.description: A trainee police officer is forced to exact her own form of justice when she’s fired and harassed for outing the colleague that raped her.

702534.title: El Cuatrero
702534.description: Con engaños, Álvaro y Mariana roban una camioneta y un caballo al ranchero Lázaro, quien los busca para recuperar sus pertenencias.

702536.title: Entre Compadres Te Veas
702536.description: Un padre y sus dos hijos deciden divertirse en el primer aniversario de la muerte de su esposa y madre y buscan aventuras en las ferias.

702670.title: Bellas De Noche
702670.description: Un boxeador retirado entra a trabajar en un centro nocturno donde se enamora de una de las bailarinas y tiene que lidiar con varios personajes.

703176.title: Money Fight
703176.description: Based on true events, this full-contact action drama, loaded with authentic mixed martial arts, is a transcending inspirational story of redemption.

703676.title: He Played Me 2
703676.description: In this sequel, Yazmin recovers and looks to move on from the aftermath of her tumultuous affair with Jai that threatened her life.

706468.title: Axl Rose: Guns N' Roses Frontman
706468.description: A documentary about the unpredictable Axl Rose, the lead vocalist of Guns N’ Roses, and how, at the height of his fame, he destroyed everything.

707798.title: Sons of a Preacher
707798.description: Chaos ensues when two brothers are forced to deal with the fallout of their decisions to answer separate callings to the streets and to God.

708103.title: Wire Room
708103.description: During surveillance, a federal agent witnesses a hit squad murder a surveillance target and soon finds himself in their crosshairs.

710214.title: Invasion of the Mermaids
710214.description: When a mysterious water monster invades a fishing community on the South China Sea, it's up to a young man to protect his fiancé and the villagers.

710949.title: Who Made the Potatoe Salad?
710949.description: A young San Diego police officers travels to Los Angeles with his fiancée to meet her dysfunctional family and announce their engagement.

711013.title: Mid90s
711013.description: A 13-year-old spends his summer navigating a troubled home life and skating with a crew of new friends.

712894.title: The Help
712894.description: In 1960s Mississippi, a Southern girl turns her small town on its ear when she interviews African-American maids who have worked for white families.

714158.title: Nasty
714158.description: Skylar is left on her own after her parents tragic accident and things start to unravel on a rollercoaster ride of love, betrayal and revenge.

714243.title: Survival Mode
714243.description: A group of close friends commit a very dangerous heist. When it's time to meet up afterward, only one of them makes it to their hideout.

714654.title: Almost Heroes
714654.description: In 1804, a habitually drunk tracker and his foppish blowhard pal lead a crew of misfits on a race to beat Lewis and Clark to the Pacific Ocean.

714949.title: Lost & Found
714949.description: To win a woman’s heart, Dylan kidnaps her dog with a plan to “find” him but a jealous ex, a missing ring and Neil Diamond throw a wrench in the works.

715989.title: Dracula: Dead and Loving It
715989.description: The vampires are loose and everyone's having a little too much fun—including the undead count himself. But professor Van Helsing is on the case.

716389.title: Poltergeist
716389.description: In this reimagining of the 1982 classic, a family fights to rescue their daughter from a demon invading their home through a portal to another world.

720992.title: Circumstances 4
720992.description: A hitman is back to end the tyranny he helped start, but his return only awakens more murder and reveals truths about who was behind it all.

722505.title: Cut Throat
722505.description: A young woman must learn to live with her new family while struggling to cope with grief and setting into motion a plan to avenge her mother's death.

723819.title: About Cherry
723819.description: A teen swaps her unsteady and unsafe homelife for a fresh start in San Francisco where she loses her innocence inside the adult film industry.

724306.title: Devil's Knot
724306.description: The rural Arkansas town of West Memphis makes national headlines when three teenagers are arrested for the brutal murders of three young boys.

724312.title: The Cleaning Lady
724312.description: A woman consumed by her love addiction to a married man befriends a disfigured cleaning woman and soon learns the terrifying origin of her scars.

724867.title: The Colony
724867.description: Forced underground by the next ice age, a struggling outpost of survivors fights to preserve humanity against a threat even more savage than nature.

725809.title: The Forbidden Daughter
725809.description: When Demetrius loses her way at a young age, an angel comes to her rescue, giving her the strength to face her fears and find her way back.

726441.title: Feral
726441.description: A vacation becomes a fight for survival when an animal attacks six medical students on a hike and turns them into rabid, bloodthirsty creatures.

100000081.title: And Then There Was You
100000081.description: A newly divorced woman who’s soured on relationships meets a new man who challenges the boundaries of her trust and her ability to fall in love again.

100000217.title: Saving Silverman
100000217.description: It takes a woman with the looks of an angel and the demeanor of the devil to test an inseparable friendship three men have shared since grade school.

100000219.title: The Smurfs
100000219.description: When evil wizard Gargamel chases the tiny blue creatures out of their village, they tumble from their magical world into the middle of Central Park.

100000265.title: Finding Love in Big Sky, Montana
100000265.description: Seeking funding to refurbish her grandfather's ranch, an independent country girl accepts help from an old boyfriend who's now a marketing exec.

100000282.title: 35 & Ticking
100000282.description: Centers around the lives of a group of friends who are approaching the age of 35 and are struggling to build the families they've always dreamed of.

100000301.title: Castaways
100000301.description: In a post apocalyptic world, two women find themselves shipwrecked on a deserted island. As they fight to survive, the experience bonds them in ways they could never have imagined.

100000406.title: Star Slammer
100000406.description: Two women fight off lesbian guards, crazed wardens, and mutant rodents as they struggle to rally their fellow inmates and escape a prison planet.

100000441.title: Gremlins
100000441.description: Billy’s furry Christmas present comes with three simple rules: keep him away from bright lights, don’t get him wet, and never feed him after midnight.

100000446.title: Butterscotch Chocolate
100000446.description: Roni is a successful lawyer, but mental illness and sex addiction threaten to throw her career off course with deadly consequences.

100000485.title: Watchful Eye
100000485.description: A group of young women enjoy their time at a Malibu beach house, unaware that the house is wired with recording equipment and they’re being watched.

100000585.title: Gone Before Her Time: Brittany Murphy
100000585.description: Scene-stealing starlet Brittany Murphy was destined for Hollywood’s A-list until her untimely and mysterious death turned out the lights on her lifelong dreams.

100000864.title: Double Threat
100000864.description: An innocent man on a trip to scatter his brother’s ashes becomes entangled with a woman on the run from the mob after a convenience store shoot-out.

100001012.title: County Line: All In
100001012.description: The murder of a crooked attorney on the county line forces two neighboring sheriffs to put aside their differences to take down the killer.

100001023.title: For Us, the Living: The Medgar Evers Story
100001023.description: The story of the NAACP’s first field secretary, whose battle for equality tragically ended with his assassination at the hand of a white supremacist.

100001225.title: Dope Girls
100001225.description: Fresh out of jail, Dee has one thing on her mind: taking over the streets. She hatches a plan to run the most powerful drug organization in the city.

100001233.title: Bestia De Nieve (Doblado)
100001233.description: Un investigador de vida silvestre y un guardabosques descubren que hay un depredador salvaje suelto en la naturaleza canadiense, y ellos son la presa.

100001250.title: Marry F*** Kill
100001250.description: After their friend Beth’s suicide, five estranged friends learn Beth bequeathed them her ancestral home - but unbeknownst to them, they’ve inherited something far more sinister.

100001362.title: Student Services
100001362.description: In order to pay for school, a broke French student becomes a massage artist and then resorts to turning tricks. Based on the steamy book by Laura D.

100001408.title: One Crazy Summer
100001408.description: During a summer in Nantucket, a recent high school grad with dreams of being a cartoonist helps a young singer save her family home from developers.

100001409.title: The Big Red One
100001409.description: Deemed one of the most powerful films ever made about World War II, this story follows a squad of sharpshooters trying not to die in the Big Red One.

100001430.title: Clara's Heart
100001430.description: A Jamaican woman teaches a boy from the Maryland suburbs about life, while his self-absorbed parents grieve over the death of their other child.

100001476.title: RocketMan
100001476.description: An accident-prone computer programmer’s childhood dream comes true when he’s selected by NASA to join the first manned mission to Mars.

100001495.title: Eight Below
100001495.description: Stranded in Antarctica due to an unforgiving winter storm, a team of sled dogs must survive together until their determined trainer can rescue them.

100001591.title: Space Jam: A New Legacy
100001591.description: When a rogue artificial intelligence kidnaps his son, LeBron James recruits the Looney Tunes to face off against the Goons in a game of basketball.

100001600.title: Crazy Rich Asians
100001600.description: Rachel travels with her boyfriend Nick to a wedding in Singapore, where she finds out his family is extremely wealthy and not very eager to meet her.

100001602.title: Godzilla
100001602.description: A mysterious creature causes a meltdown at a nuclear power plant. Years later, the monster goes on a rampage that can only be stopped by Godzilla.

100001648.title: Ojanoma
100001648.description: Sent to live with her aunt, an orphan has nothing to her name except for her great-grandmother’s magical necklace, which unlocks her true destiny.

100001652.title: Quik Money
100001652.description: After a close brush with the law, a hustler reinvents himself as a tax guru and finds himself reaping big rewards and taking on bigger risks.

100001699.title: Love Thy Neighbor
100001699.description: A suburban family lives the good life until a mysterious woman moves in next door and brings all types of problems into their lives.

100001703.title: Tyler Perry's Acrimony
100001703.description: A faithful wife tired of standing by her devious husband is enraged when it becomes clear she has been betrayed by him financially.

100001712.title: Detective Knight: Redemption
100001712.description: In the trilogy’s second film, Detective James Knight deals with mercy and justice on his terms when The Christmas Bomber terrorizes the city.

100001957.title: Pulso
100001957.description: Tras contraer el VIH en un tórrido romance, un marido infiel parte en busca de su ex amante y no parará hasta vengarse de ella por lo sucedido.

100001975.title: Breaking Fast
100001975.description: Mo, a practicing Muslim doctor who is openly gay, is getting over a breakup. Enter Kal, an actor who breaks fast with Mo every night during Ramadan.

100002033.title: You Never Know
100002033.description: Immersed in a world filled with crime, drugs, and betrayal, a group of friends find themselves in too deep when they’re interrogated by a detective.

100002054.title: Look Again
100002054.description: After a young woman's boyfriend is murdered by an intruder, things worsen when she meets her friend's new boyfriend and suspects him to be the killer.

100002134.title: Flesh Wounds
100002134.description: On a remote U.S. Army facility, an elite covert operations team is tasked with recovering a missing group of scientists within 24 hours.

100002155.title: A Body to Kill For
100002155.description: Growing up in Philadelphia, China enjoys a life of privilege until a handsome suitor exposes her to a dark side of the city that changes her forever.

100002612.title: The Exhibitionist
100002612.description: A love triangle leads to heartbreak when a gigolo returns to sex work at a sophisticated nightclub, only to fall for the stepdaughter of his mistress.

100002686.title: TMZ Presents: Megan vs. Tory: What REALLY Went Down
100002686.description: TMZ dives into the events following the shooting of Meg Thee Stallion by fellow rapper Tory Lanez, including reaction online and the showdown in court.

100002715.title: Bermuda Island
100002715.description: Passengers on their way to a tropical paradise crash at sea and find themselves on a deserted island. Desperate to survive the elements and infighting between survivors, they find that the island has more in store for them than they could ever imagine.

0300009901.title: Lovecraft Country
0300009901.description: Atticus Freema joins his friend Letitia and his uncle George to embark on a road trip across 1950's Jim Crow America in search of his missing father.

0300006625.title: Charlie's Angels
0300006625.description: Three smart, stunning women use their lethal feminine charms and combat skills as PIs, assigned to crack cases via speakerphone by a mysterious boss.

0300010409.title: Taken
0300010409.description: While dealing with a personal tragedy that shakes his world, CIA agent Bryan Mills fights to overcome the incident and exact revenge.

0300010125.title: Underground
0300010125.description: An unflinching story of plantation slaves who band together for the fight of their lives—for their families, their future, and their freedom.

0300007812.title: Gordon Ramsay's 24 Hours to Hell and Back
0300007812.description: Celebrity chef Gordon Ramsay and his second-in-command have just 24 hours to bring struggling restaurants back from the brink of disaster.

0300005346.title: The Son (Español)
0300005346.description: La lucha del "primer hijo de Texas" por establecerse como un poderoso ganadero y su posterior incursión en la naciente industria del petróleo.

0300004913.title: Mafia Killers
0300004913.description: Colin McLaren shares stories about his undercover work inside organized crime families; chilling firsthand details about how mafia families operate and why their ruthlessness was often their downfall.

0300000091.title: Rogue
0300000091.description: Undercover detective Grace Travis' involvement with the city’s most powerful and dangerous crime family causes her to pay the ultimate price.

0300007350.title: Hollywood Divas
0300007350.description: From image issues to being blackballed over their love lives, five famous TV actresses try to make a comeback in Tinseltown despite their clashes.

0300010224.title: Scarecrow and Mrs. King
0300010224.description: A single mother in suburban Washington, D.C. discovers she has a talent for espionage work when she meets a dashing undercover agent.

0300010040.title: Serial Killer With Piers Morgan
0300010040.description: In this thrilling series, television personality Piers Morgan meets and interviews some of America’s most depraved serial killers.

0300004999.title: Garfield and Friends
0300004999.description: Lazy, lasagna-loving cat Garfield has fun adventures with his pal Odie and owner Jon.

0300007078.title: Soap
0300007078.description: A satire on soap operas, this zany comedy threw together a group of family members whose lives were larger than life and never dull! Stories take some bizarre and unexpected turns as the daily living of the wealthy Tate family and the blue-collar Campbell family unfold.

02348.title: Duck Dynasty
02348.description: Follow the Robertsons as they run a multi-million dollar sporting empire and face everything from beavers to business deals, in this reality series.

0300008639.title: The Steve Harvey Show
0300008639.description: Steve Harvey's sitcom from the WB network is classic '90s comedy about a musician-turned-teacher who teaches his unruly students a thing or three!

0300000124.title: Gilligan's Island
0300000124.description: Shipwrecked on an uncharted South Pacific island, seven castaways struggle to survive the outdoors—and each other—in this wacky classic comedy series.

0300008984.title: Da Vinci’s Demons
0300008984.description: Tortured young genius, artist, and inventor, Leonardo Da Vinci, defies authority and throws himself into the future, changing the fate of humanity.

0300009077.title: The Temptations
0300009077.description: This touching miniseries brings to life the true story behind the legendary Motown musical sensation of the 60s, the r&b vocal group the Temptations.

0300000087.title: Deputy
0300000087.description: When an elected sheriff dies, an arcane rule in the county charter, forged back in the Wild West, suddenly thrusts the most unlikely man into the job.

0300007447.title: The World's Strangest Mysteries
0300007447.description: Footage of UFO's, mysterious anomalies, paranormal sightings, weird discoveries in space, and bizarre case files form a library of the unexplainable.

0300009557.title: El Mariachi
0300009557.description: A través de una serie de circunstancias desafortunadas, un músico de mariachi descubre que lo buscan por un asesinato que no cometió.

0300008306.title: Next Level Chef
0300008306.description: Celebrity chef Gordon Ramsay hosts ambitious chefs facing unique cooking challenges, in a culinary competition to be the food world’s next superstar.

0300006628.title: Hart to Hart
0300006628.description: Wealthy, amorous, stylish supersleuths Jonathan and Jennifer Hart, roam the world, hobnob with the rich and famous, and solve crimes along the way

04091.title: La Promesa
04091.description: Son jóvenes, hermosas y presas fáciles de una red de gente sin escrúpulos que prometen una vida soñada y solo trafica con mercancía humana.

0300006728.title: Columbo
0300006728.description: This beloved series features the brilliant bumbling detective who despite his easygoing nature, always manages to crack the case.

0300000074.title: Alaska Monsters
0300000074.description: A team of outdoorsmen hunt for cryptic creatures in the Alaska Triangle, a treacherous 200,000-mile region known for unusual disappearances.

0300010071.title: Babylon 5
0300010071.description: 2258 CE. The lone space station Babylon 5 stands as the last and best hope for peace between a hundred worlds, alien and human alike.

03697.title: V
03697.description: When human-looking aliens known as Visitors appear in every major city U.S. promoting peace, an FBI counter-terrorist discovers their deadly plot.

0300004988.title: Fugget About It
0300004988.description: A former New York mobster joins the Witness Protection Program, which relocates him and his family, who must adjust to life in Saskatchewan, Canada.

0300009028.title: Leave It to Beaver
0300009028.description: The beloved series from TV’s Golden Era sees the world of a loving American family through the eyes of a young boy, who cannot seem to avoid trouble.

0300009559.title: Farscape
0300009559.description: Thrown into a distant part of the universe, an Earth astronaut finds himself part of a fugitive alien starship crew.

0300009020.title: The Transporter
0300009020.description: A woman, chosen to be the driver for one of the biggest drug operations in the world, must outdrive and outshoot enemies, in fabulous, exotic locales.

0300005157.title: Super Wings
0300005157.description: The action-packed preschool series features an adorable jet, who travels the world with his amazing plane pals, delivering packages to kids.

0300006854.title: Scooby-Doo Where Are You?
0300006854.description: The classic adventures of the lovable Great Dane and his human companions as they hunt for clues, hungry for a solution to mysteries and a snack.

0300008551.title: Sue Thomas: F.B.Eye
0300008551.description: Inspired by a true story, a deaf woman uses her lip-reading skills and trusty dog to help an FBI surveillance team bring bad guys to justice.

0300010309.title: Swamp Murders
0300010309.description: This series reveals the salacious stories behind bodies found in swamps. Featuring reenactments and interviews with people involved in each case.

0300009281.title: Everybody Hates Chris
0300009281.description: Comedian Chris Rock narrates the hilarious, touching story of a teenager growing up as the eldest of three children in Brooklyn during the 1980s.

0300010281.title: Breaking Amish
0300010281.description: Follow young adults from the Amish and Mennonite communities as they leave their homes to experiment with "new world" freedoms in New York City.

0300009326.title: Señorita Pólvora
0300009326.description: La historia de una mujer bella que se enamora de un sicario. Sin embargo, descubre que su querido pertenece a uno de los cárteles más poderosos.

0300010397.title: How It's Made
0300010397.description: This series explores the fascinating world of how everyday items are manufactured and produced—anything from toothpicks, to pantyhose, to gummy candy.

0300007629.title: Meet, Marry, Murder
0300007629.description: Wedded couples vow to stay together, until death do they part. This series looks at what happens when a bride or groom causes their beloved’s demise.
